snippet.title: Humbled Trader
snippet.description:
Hi! My name is Humbled Trader.

Are you tired of all the Lambos, the luxury travel and partying you see in ads for day trading chat rooms and related services?

I am too! And I promise you won't see any of that here. This is a channel made by a day trader for day traders who are REAL. Stock market trading and investing is hard. Seeing all the fluff out there on social media creates unrealistic expectations for beginners new to day trading. 

Here's what you will get here:
-Realistic day trading strategies
-Penny stock trading strategies
-Swing trading overnight set ups
-How to read SEC filings for penny stocks
-How to day trade sympathies and hypes for both large caps and small cap penny stocks!
-Day trading breakout and breakdown on large caps

If you want to see some real, and condensed content for both beginners and experienced, SUBSCRIBE for more! :)

For business inquiries only, you can reach me at HumbledTraderBusiness(at)gmail.com
